Sentece: Extravascular administration significantly increased mean serum interferon alfa-n3 AUC values (1152 +/- 214, 944 +/- 209, and 576 +/- 188 U.h/mL, p < 0.001, with SQ, i.m., and i.v. administration, respectively) and 2-5(A) synthetase activity at 36 and 48 hours after dosing.
Title: Extravascular administration of interferon alfa-N3 increases serum exposure and 2-5(A) synthetase activity.
Name: Interferon alfa-n3
